config BR2_PACKAGE_AETHERSX2
    bool "aethersx2"
    depends on BR2_aarch64
    depends on BR2_PACKAGE_HAS_GLES3 || BR2_PACKAGE_BATOCERA_VULKAN

 

    help
      Aethersx2 is an aarch64 closed source fork of PCSX2 Playstaion 2 emulator.

      This package installs the official prebuilt Aethersx2 AppImage
      instead of building aethersx2 from source.

     
